result.name: Qian Shao Bai Wei

reviews.text: This is the usual restaurant I visit for my meals before leaving Hong Kong at the airport.  Reasonably-priced Chinese fastfood restaurant at Chek Lap Kok airport serving real meals.  There are enough seats for 40+ diners at any one time. Some waiting (about 10 minutes max.) for your order to be done in the kitchen.

A place where both airport staffs and passengers like to go. Breakfast start as early as 06:30 a.m. There are a wide variety of choice for breakfast with reasonable price. It is self service and expect 10 to 15  minutes to queue up for food after you paid at the cashier.

One bite of the tender, succulent, richly flavored BBQ pork (asado) and you know you've arrived in Hong Kong. Amazing softness and flavor, as only Hong Kong can do it. I was much less impressed with their other roast staples however. Roasted goose and white chicken tasted so-so.
In fact, price is not high in that cafe.
Good meal before the flight. Price is also rational.

reviews.text: This is the usual restaurant I visit for my meals before leaving Hong Kong at the airport.  Reasonably-priced Chinese fastfood restaurant at Chek Lap Kok airport serving real meals.  There are enough seats for 40+ diners at any one time. Some waiting (about 10 minutes max.) for your order to be done in the kitchen.

午餐燒味飯味道不錯，早餐選擇也很多，雜扒早餐是這裏最熱賣的一款。
而糯米雞是我較為喜愛吃的早點，用料和味道比其他連鎖快餐店的好上不少喔！
價錢合理。地方整潔。工作人員有禮
香港空港についたらまずこのレストランに行きます。バスターミナル側にいくとレストランがたくさん並んでいますが、いつもこのお店だけお客様でいっぱいです。香港市内にいかなくても香港らしい美味しい料理を食べられます。オススメはご飯の上に鴨が乗っている料理と、アイスレモンティです。
下午離港前過來醫個肚，做為一個港味的留念！
